We are at the press and... praise God.

411
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:40,000
Hemdillah.
 
Praise God.

412
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,000
Saetê ta xweş Xalo, Xwedê emrê ke dirêj bide te.
 
Thank you Uncle, may God give you a long life.

413
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,000
