Mashallah, mashallah... what an atmosphere.

432
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:15,000
Abu Fayîq, ey se pişta xanî teme ho.
 
Abu Faiq, hey look I am behind your house, look.

433
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:23,000
Maşallah.
 
Mashallah.

