514
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:18,000
Em kanin stranekê ji gindê...
 
Can we [hear] a song from the village...

515
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:25,000
Mipşkîlat nîne, ser dil û jigera, ser çava.
 
No problem, upon my heart and soul, upon my eyes.

516
